headline: Strong Earnings Beat and Raised Guidance Could Be a Game Changer for Quest Diagnostics (DGX)
summary: Earlier this week, Quest Diagnostics reported third-quarter earnings exceeding expectations, raised its full-year guidance, and expanded its partnership and acquisition activity to further grow its diagnostic services business. Notably, Quest’s results were supported by strong year-over-year revenue and net income growth, reflecting rising demand, operational efficiency, and investments in technology and partnerships that aim to broaden its offering and reach.
